data.description: Introducing 11619 Pelican Pass - a remarkable 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom haven designed for the ultimate in comfort and luxury. This QUALITY BUILT DR HORTON HOME named The Glick stands as a testament to superior craftsmanship. Step into the expansive living area, seamlessly connected to the kitchen and breakfast nook, creating a welcoming space for family gatherings and entertaining. The kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, is as stylish as it is functional, offering ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. Appliances include a dishwasher, range, and microwave, ensuring convenience in every culinary venture. The focal point of the living room is a magnificent stone fireplace, adding warmth and charm to the space. What sets this home apart are the dual master bedrooms-one conveniently located downstairs and another upstairs. The downstairs master bath boasts a garden tub, separate shower, dual vanities, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Ascend the stairs to discover the second master bedroom with its own ensuite, providing versatility and privacy. The allure continues outside, where a covered patio invites you to relax and enjoy the serene surroundings. Situated on a GREENBELT LOT, this residence offers an added layer of privacy, creating a peaceful retreat. 11619 Pelican Pass is not just a house; it's a well-crafted home designed for those who appreciate quality and distinction. Seize the opportunity to make this exceptional property yours today!
